# UI Design System

## Visual Direction
Model every page after a modern marketplace / Gumroad-style aesthetic: clean white cards on a warm off-white background, strong black borders, content-first layout, minimal chrome. The signature interaction is the "elevated" hover — elements lift up with a hard black box-shadow AND a physical translate. Pink is the accent color, always paired with black.

## Core Rules
- Background body: `bg-[#F4F4F0]` — warm off-white. NEVER pure white on body
- Cards: `bg-white rounded-md border overflow-hidden h-full flex flex-col`
- Card hover: `hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-shadow`
- Elevated hover (buttons): `hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all`
- All borders are **black** by default (set via CSS variable `--border: oklch(0 0 0)` and `--input: oklch(0 0 0)`)
- Primary accent color: `bg-pink-400` (price badges, active states, hover accent)
- Primary CTA buttons: `bg-black text-white hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary`
- Secondary/elevated buttons: `variant="elevated"` — white background that lifts on hover
- Font: **DM Sans** — import via `next/font/google`
- NEVER use dark mode classes on public or judge pages (light theme only)
- NEVER use inline styles — Tailwind only (except dynamic background colors)

## CSS Variables (globals.css)
These override shadcn defaults to achieve the black-border aesthetic:
```css
:root {
  --border: oklch(0 0 0);        /* Black borders everywhere */
  --input: oklch(0 0 0);         /* Black input borders */
  --ring: oklch(0.708 0 0);      /* Focus ring */
  --primary: oklch(0.205 0 0);   /* Near-black primary */
  --primary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --secondary: oklch(0.97 0 0);
  --muted-foreground: oklch(0.556 0 0);
}
```

## Button Variants
The `elevated` variant is the signature interaction — use shadcn Button with this custom variant:
```tsx
// In components/ui/button.tsx, add this variant:
elevated: "bg-white hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all"

// Default button height is h-12 (taller than typical)
```

### CRITICAL: Every Button Gets Elevated Hover
**EVERY interactive button MUST include the elevated hover effect.** No flat, lifeless buttons anywhere.
The full elevated hover classes are:
```
hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all
```
For small icon buttons or card-footer actions, use a smaller lift:
```
hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] transition-all
```

### Button Recipes (copy-paste these exactly)
```tsx
// 1. Primary CTA — black with pink hover + elevated lift
<button className="px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium bg-black text-white rounded-md border border-black hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all">
  Create Event
</button>

// 2. Or using shadcn Button:
<Button variant="elevated" className="bg-black text-white hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary">
  Create Event
</Button>

// 3. Secondary / Cancel — white elevated lift
<button className="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border rounded-md bg-white hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all">
  Cancel
</button>

// 4. Destructive — red with elevated lift
<button className="px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-red-600 text-white rounded-md border border-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all">
  Delete
</button>

// 5. Small icon button (card footers, table actions)
<button className="p-1.5 rounded-md border bg-white hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] transition-all">
  <Pencil className="size-3.5 text-muted-foreground" />
</button>

// 6. Small text button with icon (card footers)
<button className="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium border rounded-md bg-white text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px] transition-all">
  <Plus className="size-3.5" /> Add Item
</button>

// 7. Inline table action
<button className="px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-black text-white rounded hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
  Approve
</button>

// 8. Navbar auth button — full height, border-left, rounded-none
<Button className="border-l border-t-0 border-b-0 border-r-0 px-12 h-full rounded-none bg-black text-white hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-black transition-colors text-lg">
  Dashboard
</Button>

// 9. Sort/filter pill — rounded-full
<Button size="sm" variant="secondary" className="rounded-full bg-white hover:bg-white">
  Active Tab
</Button>

// 10. Toggle selector (e.g. JSS / Senior)
<button className={cn(
  "flex-1 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium border rounded-md transition-all",
  isActive
    ? "bg-black text-white border-black shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]"
    : "bg-white text-muted-foreground hover:border-black hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px]"
)}>
  Option
</button>
```

### Modal / Dialog Button Pattern
Dialog footers ALWAYS follow this layout:
```tsx
<div className="flex justify-end gap-2 pt-2">
  {/* Cancel — white elevated */}
  <button className="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border rounded-md bg-white hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all">
    Cancel
  </button>
  {/* Confirm — black CTA elevated */}
  <button className="px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium bg-black text-white rounded-md border border-black hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] hover:-translate-x-[4px] hover:-translate-y-[4px] transition-all disabled:opacity-50">
    Confirm
  </button>
</div>
```

## Standard Card Pattern
```tsx
<div className="hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-shadow border rounded-md bg-white overflow-hidden h-full flex flex-col">
