## Typography Scale
- Page hero title: `text-4xl font-medium` or `text-[40px] font-medium`
- Page title: `text-2xl font-medium`
- Card headline: `text-lg font-medium line-clamp-4`
- Section label: `text-base font-medium`
- Body / form labels: `text-base font-medium` (larger than default)
- Secondary/meta: `text-sm font-medium`
- Underlined links: `underline font-medium`
- Muted text: `text-muted-foreground`

## Input / Form Styling
Inputs are taller and bolder than shadcn defaults:
```tsx
// In components/ui/input.tsx, add these modified classes:
"h-12 bg-white font-medium md:text-base"

// Form labels should be text-base (not the tiny default):
<FormLabel className="text-base">Email</FormLabel>
```

## Avatars & Icons
- Small avatars: `rounded-full border shrink-0 size-[16px]`
- Medium avatars: `rounded-full border shrink-0 size-[20px]`
- Icon + text: `flex items-center gap-1` or `gap-2`
- Inline icons: `size-3.5`
- Button icons: `size-4`
- Filled icons: `fill-black` (e.g. StarIcon)

