## Layout Rules
- Page wrapper: `px-4 lg:px-12 py-8` (generous horizontal padding)
- Centered narrow content: `max-w-2xl mx-auto`
- Card grids: `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 2xl:grid-cols-4 gap-4`
- Sidebar + content: `grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-6 xl:grid-cols-8 gap-y-6 gap-x-12`
- Filter sidebar: `lg:col-span-2 xl:col-span-2`
- Main content: `lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-6`
- Stacked sections: `flex flex-col gap-4`
- Filter rows: `flex items-center gap-2`
- Section dividers: `border-b` (black by default)
- Content area background: `bg-[#F4F4F0]`

