## Component Rules
- Always use `cn()` from lib/utils for conditional classNames
- Import shadcn components from `@/components/ui/`
- Never build a custom input/button/dialog from scratch — always use shadcn first
- Lucide icons only — no other icon libraries
- All text should use `font-medium` unless specifically muted
- Links that navigate should be `underline font-medium`
- **EVERY button MUST have the elevated hover** — shadow lift + translate. No flat buttons anywhere.
- Use `variant="elevated"` for interactive cards and secondary actions
- Use `bg-black text-white hover:bg-pink-400 hover:text-primary` for primary CTAs
- Cancel buttons get `bg-white` with elevated lift
- Destructive buttons get red bg with elevated lift
- Small card-footer buttons use the smaller `hover:-translate-x-[2px] hover:-translate-y-[2px]` lift
- Active toggle states get `shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]` to show depth
- Always use `transition-all` (not `transition-colors`) on buttons so the translate + shadow animates